{"tid":1661063,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依加係咪可以放心打狗啦？？？","createTime":"2019-10-18T01:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T06:53:00.000Z","uid":73392,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4df60a7bb43b1b668c76172ce6f965bd545f0b27","tid":1661063,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"一直以來有速龍，防暴，大家都係走，好主要原因嘅真係打起上黎，黑警可以出槍，咁我地就好危險，好似健仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依加有左又平，又防彈嘅物料，只要買一塊大塊嘅做盾，一手攞鐵棍，長矛，一大堆盾劍打近戰，黑警開槍都未必有優勢嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658039</a><br />\n<br />\n打狗救人再唔係遙不可及了，可能黑警會比大家輕鬆反殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cef0e9110ac28114d057dc5ef08280631f97980","tid":1661063,"uid":73392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"你可能會講：咁如果黑警出步槍咁實死啦"},{"pid":"70fa89860c6c000b79dfa44bbc0aff5f6c871e1f","tid":1661063,"uid":73392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"冇錯黑警出步槍真係未必頂得住，但係出步槍，有極大機會打死人，而且係各大傳媒下嘅鏡頭下比鏡到"},{"pid":"49877548114fedc3466828ce0e69fbb716f422f5","tid":1661063,"uid":73392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"咁你估歐美列強會就手旁觀嗎？"},{"pid":"4b86f6d9ed87d7bfd8e6844a47f71ee82b37a388","tid":1661063,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07a1e8ae25a5cf5424edd63ce67bf49d3d4716f0","tid":1661063,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"出步槍嘅話<br />\n應該會有軍隊介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n確定好步槍同指彈夠貨未"},{"pid":"628e7005e